data.description: Welcome to this stunning 4 bedroom Colonial custom home nestled in the prestigious Oak Hill subdivision. Boasting beautiful landscaping, this residence is a true masterpiece of design and craftsmanship. The exterior features a three-car garage, adding both convenience and style to the property. Step inside, and you'll be greeted by the grand open foyer, open concept floor plan, granite countertops and a spacious kitchen with an island in the heart of the home. As you explore further, discover the luxurious theater room in the finished basement, providing the perfect space for entertainment and relaxation. The basement is equipped to add a 5th bedroom and bathroom. This home is a true gem, don't wait to make house your home today!
